item.title: CVE-2021-36276|2024-09-17T02:42:58.797Z -- dell -- dbutil
item.description: Dell DBUtilDrv2.sys driver (versions 2.5 and 2.6) contains an insufficient access control vulnerability which may lead to escalation of privileges, denial of service, or information disclosure. Local authenticated user access is required.
